    "9 Proposal for a Regulation of The European Parliament and of the Council Laying Down Harmonised Rules on Artificial Intelligence (Artificial Intelligence Act) and Amending Certain Union Legislative Acts COM/2021/206 final.",
    "10 See for a discussion Buiten et al. (2023) and Hacker (2023).",
    "11 Next to the definition of defect, the PLD Proposal aims to clarify among other things the definition of product and the liable party.",
    "It also makes changes to the available defences, the burden of proof and the categories of damages.",
    "This section begins by examining the overarching economic justification for implementing product liability in cases involving harm to third parties and customers."
